        <h1>🐱 About Cats</h1>

        <p>

            Cats are one of the most popular pets in the world because they are
            intelligent, affectionate, and independent companions. Every cat
            breed has its own personality, appearance, activity level, and care
            requirements. Learning about different breeds helps future pet
            owners choose a cat that best fits their lifestyle.

        </p>

    </div>

    <br>

