        <h2>🌍 Cat Breeds Around the World</h2>

        <p>

            Cat breeds originate from many countries including Egypt,
            Thailand, Russia, Norway, the United Kingdom, and the United States.
            Each breed has unique physical characteristics and temperament,
            making every breed special in its own way.

        </p>

    </div>

